Package: LuccPL
Title: Processing and analisys language for land use and cover changes
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: person("Carlos", "Romani", email = "car13romani@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package aims to perform a series of analyzes on spatio-temporal data on land use, in order 
to assist in the observation of changes that occur over time.
